'''Monofilament nets''' were virtually invisible<ref name="GA2">{{WEGCite|book=Classic Adventures: Volume Two|story=Graveyard of Alderaan}}</ref> traps. They were composed of multiple strands of razor-sharp [[monofilament wire]]. These nets shredded virtually anything that came into contact with them. The people of [[Anobis]] used monofilament nets during their civil war.<ref name="ROM">''[[Young Jedi Knights: Return to Ord Mantell]]''</ref> However, not all monofilament nets were lethal. At least one net was used as a safety net in the remains of the [[Royal Palace of Alderaan/Legends|Grand Hall]] in the [[Royal Palace of Alderaan/Legends|Aldera Royal Palace]]. Individuals falling into the net had their fall broken to stop them from descending into a pit.<ref name="GA2" />

